{"tid":1915512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，呢度我屋企嚟㗎","createTime":"2020-03-08T09:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T13:41:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9520cb4d85948307c668d8f6d3eefce18e543ad3","tid":1915512,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:08:16.000Z","msg":"Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n&middot; 2 mins &middot;<br />\n <br />\n【1658 大埔】<br />\n<br />\n今日有市民發起遊行反對大埔的指定診所，防暴警員到場制服多人，並多次施放胡椒噴霧。<br />\n<br />\n一名男子站在海寶花園平台，觀察下方的拘捕情況時，有警員廣播要求「影住上面個男人」，男子以粗口回敬：「X你老母，呢度我屋企嚟㗎」，獲現場市民拍手歡呼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2910323582386576/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F2910323582386576%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=11237bf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/2910323582386576/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/88961752_2910323585719909_3508666497587216384_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=MDZ5qEeVlOkAX8f-Rqk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=687e8c9523e9c4d979648e1b9dea3f36&amp;oe=5E80AD0E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F88961752_2910323585719909_3508666497587216384_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DMDZ5qEeVlOkAX8f-Rqk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D687e8c9523e9c4d979648e1b9dea3f36%26oe%3D5E80AD0E&h=79b356f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4144e4fdabaa37ac9551e58c6797a377ac6c792c","tid":1915512,"uid":161025,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jLuvY5U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjLuvY5U.png&h=c7e17acd&s=